{
  "title": "About Timeline Plugin",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "1592fc065c5f2177",
      "text": "The Timeline Plugin renders a navigable SVG timeline. It collects events from [[About Date Plugin]] items upstream in the lineup and from events authored directly in the item text."
    },
    {
      "type": "timeline",
      "id": "34db669a30ee58c9",
      "text": "section Demoscene\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-01-15 Hitchhiker Game Jam\n\nsection Projects\n2025-04-12 Patchable Knowledge Habitats"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "26zn6d0j",
      "text": "## Examples"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "htnw67t1",
      "text": "**Point events** — named milestones on a shared axis"
    },
    {
      "type": "timeline",
      "id": "74zdahyg",
      "text": "2026-01-15 Project Kickoff\n2026-02-28 First Prototype\n2026-04-10 User Testing\n2026-05-20 Beta Release\n2026-06-30 Launch"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "3wdyh6k9",
      "text": "**Range events** — spans of time with a start and end"
    },
    {
      "type": "timeline",
      "id": "e4j875tc",
      "text": "2026-01-01..2026-01-31 Research\n2026-02-01..2026-04-30 Development\n2026-05-01..2026-05-31 Beta Testing\n2026-06-01..2026-06-30 Launch Window"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ogk4i32o",
      "text": "**Sections** — group events into labelled swimlanes using `section`"
    },
    {
      "type": "timeline",
      "id": "u80qm53u",
      "text": "section Demoscene\n2026-02-10 First Demo\n2026-03-20..2026-03-22 Demoparty\n2026-05-15 Release\n\nsection Fedwiki\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-06-15 Judging"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "palette-intro",
      "text": "**Palette** — colour the whole diagram with `PALETTE`"
    },
    {
      "type": "timeline",
      "id": "palette-warm",
      "text": "PALETTE warm\nsection Demoscene\n2026-02-10 First Demo\n2026-03-20..2026-03-22 Demoparty\n2026-05-15 Release\n\nsection Fedwiki\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-06-15 Judging"
    },
    {
      "type": "timeline",
      "id": "palette-neon",
      "text": "PALETTE neon\nsection Demoscene\n2026-02-10 First Demo\n2026-03-20..2026-03-22 Demoparty\n2026-05-15 Release\n\nsection Fedwiki\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-06-15 Judging"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "db26ae488c281829",
      "text": "## DSL"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "72a9df6bb9cddc6c",
      "text": "One event per line, Mermaid gantt-inspired syntax:"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "16ad471df6e2cefd",
      "text": "LINEUP\n\nsection Demoscene\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-01-15 Hitchhiker Game Jam #Demos"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "650016c2aec35a63",
      "text": "| Keyword | Meaning |\n|---|---|\n| `LINEUP` | Scan upstream `.calendar-source` items for events |\n| `PALETTE name` | Apply a named palette: `default` `warm` `cool` `earth` `mono` `neon` |\n| `PALETTE #hex …` | Apply custom hex colours (space-separated) |\n| `PALETTE colour …` | Apply named colours: `red` `blue` `green` `orange` `purple` `teal` `pink` `cyan` `indigo` `lime` `amber` `violet` `rose` `navy` `brown` `grey` `yellow` |\n| `section Name` | Start a named group lane |\n| `YYYY-MM-DD Label` | Point event |\n| `YYYY-MM-DD..YYYY-MM-DD Label` | Range event |\n| `#GroupName` | Inline group tag (overrides current section) |"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "e0b03a5b3caa237d",
      "text": "## Navigation\n\nClicking an event calls `wiki.doInternalLink` with the event label as the page title. The label must match a reachable wiki page title. Shift-click opens the page in a new column."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ebe4455f741e7246",
      "text": "## Freeze-Thaw\n\nClick ❄ to snapshot the current lineup events into `item.frozen`. The timeline becomes self-contained — no lineup scan needed. Shift-click ❄ to restore live scanning.\n\n## Fullscreen\n\nClick ⤢ to open the timeline in a popup with pan (drag) and zoom (scroll wheel)."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "c0268fe5f609f699",
      "text": "## Repositories\n\n* [GitHub — wiki-plugin-timeline](https://github.com/Hitchhikers-Guide-to-the-Galaxy/wiki-plugin-timeline)\n* [npm — wiki-plugin-timeline](https://www.npmjs.com/package/wiki-plugin-timeline)"
    }
  ],
